## Token Reference (WCPItemTile CSS)

| Element | Token |
|---|---|
| Tile background | `var(--ld-semantic-color-surface)` |
| Border radius | `var(--ld-primitive-scale-borderradius-100)` |
| Price text (default) | `var(--ld-semantic-color-text)` |
| Price text (savings) | `var(--ld-semantic-color-text-positive)` |
| Original price text | `var(--ld-semantic-color-text-subtle)` |
| Product name | `var(--ld-semantic-color-text)` |
| Font family | `var(--ld-semantic-font-family-sans)` |

