## Accessibility

- Heart button includes `aria-label` ("Add to favorites" / "Remove from favorites") and `aria-pressed`
- Product image includes `alt` text set to the product name
- Product name is clamped to 1 line with `text-overflow: ellipsis` — full name is accessible via the `alt` attribute on the image
- Flag badge is rendered as a `<span>` with visible text — screen readers can read the badge label

