## Pre-Implementation Checklist

Before creating any new item tile usage or variant:

- [ ] Using `WCPItemTile` — not a custom tile component
- [ ] Badge type exists in `ItemTileBadgeType` union
- [ ] Images sourced from `PRODUCT_IMAGES` constant
- [ ] Parent grid uses `grid-auto-rows: 1fr` for equal height
- [ ] Heart uses `size="small"` and `calloutPosition="top"`
- [ ] All colors use semantic tokens (no hardcoded hex)
- [ ] Price layout follows the two defined variants (default or savings)
- [ ] Component library page updated if new variant added
